00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:04,720
Yes!

272
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:08,200
♪ Make the first move and never give up ♪

273
00:18:08,280 --> 00:18:11,720
♪ Let the blood inside you flow ♪

274
00:18:12,120 --> 00:18:13,360
You still have a long way to go.

275
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:18,800
♪ Young face, heaving chest ♪

276
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:22,320
♪ As always
I'll chase my dreams like I used to ♪

277
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:26,000
♪ Swallow my tears
And make myself stronger ♪

278
00:18:26,080 --> 00:18:29,080
♪ Sweat illuminating in the hot sun ♪

279
00:18:29,160 --> 00:18:31,680
♪ Dear youth ♪

280
00:18:31,760 --> 00:18:32,880
♪ Dear youth ♪

281
00:18:34,120 --> 00:18:36,000
YU QING WINNER

282
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:38,800
♪ Dear youth ♪

283
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:40,000
♪ Dear youth ♪

284
00:18:40,080 --> 00:18:43,200
♪ Don't be afraid, work hard and grow up ♪

285
00:18:43,280 --> 00:18:46,800
♪ We are in the best years of youth ♪

286
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:50,360
♪ We should seize the day ♪

287
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:52,600
♪ Live the way ♪

288
00:18:52,680 --> 00:18:56,200
♪ You want to live the most ♪

289
00:18:56,280 --> 00:18:58,680
Xing Yao still has a chance
to play in the national league.

290
00:18:59,320 --> 00:19:00,360
I hope...

291
00:19:01,320 --> 00:19:02,400
we can meet again.

292
00:19:03,800 --> 00:19:04,960
I'm looking forward to it.

293
00:19:05,840 --> 00:19:06,720
All right.

294
00:19:07,200 --> 00:19:08,760
Hurry up and go to the hospital.

295
00:19:09,520 --> 00:19:11,480
You can call me if you need any help.

296
00:19:12,360 --> 00:19:13,280
Okay.

297
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:14,920
Thank you.

298
00:19:15,800 --> 00:19:19,520
OUTPATIENT SERVICE

299
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:27,920
[sighs]

300
00:19:30,040 --> 00:19:32,760
Do you think

301
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:34,760
-the captain's arm...
-Shut up.

302
00:19:38,280 --> 00:19:39,920
[gasps]
How is he?

303
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:42,160
Who will go upstairs
to get Mu Siyang's film?

304
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:43,200
[both] I will go.

305
00:19:53,320 --> 00:19:54,560
[sighs]

306
00:19:56,760 --> 00:19:57,880
[exhales sharply]

307
00:20:01,080 --> 00:20:02,840
-Jiale.
-Hmm?

308
00:20:04,760 --> 00:20:07,520
I wasn't there today.

309
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:09,960
I'm sorry.

310
00:20:10,280 --> 00:20:11,120
For what?

311
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:12,200
This is not your fault.

312
00:20:12,280 --> 00:20:13,400
What are you apologizing for?

313
00:20:13,560 --> 00:20:15,760
It's just an accident.
It was beyond your expectation.

314
00:20:18,240 --> 00:20:22,520
Or is it because you just overslept
like Lu Xia,

315
00:20:22,600 --> 00:20:24,480
and made an excuse to fool us?

316
00:20:24,680 --> 00:20:25,520
[sighs]

317
00:20:25,920 --> 00:20:27,120
It was true. I helped her.

318
00:20:27,280 --> 00:20:28,760
And my old wounds recrudesced.

319
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:30,800
Then it's okay.

320
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:32,800
But I'm scared to stand

321
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:34,760
on the court with you

322
00:20:35,760 --> 00:20:37,080
even before that.

323
00:20:37,600 --> 00:20:39,600
[dramatic music]

324
00:20:40,600 --> 00:20:41,520
Why?

325
00:20:43,760 --> 00:20:45,640
Because you improved so fast.

326
00:20:46,520 --> 00:20:50,800
[Dayong] At first, I can be your shield
on the frontcourt.

327
00:20:51,560 --> 00:20:55,520
But I became your burden when you run.

328
00:20:56,560 --> 00:20:57,680
[Tang Jiale] Chi Dayong.

329
00:20:57,760 --> 00:21:00,760
You are not my shield or my burden.

330
00:21:02,160 --> 00:21:03,360
You are my partner.

331
00:21:03,680 --> 00:21:04,920
You are Yu Qing's main player.

332
00:21:05,360 --> 00:21:06,480
You are our vice-captain.

333
00:21:14,400 --> 00:21:15,360
Dachi.

334
00:21:17,800 --> 00:21:19,240
I can accept your apology.

335
00:21:20,280 --> 00:21:22,440
But you have to promise...

336
00:21:24,400 --> 00:21:25,840
that you won't leave me alone...

337
00:21:28,040 --> 00:21:29,320
whatever happens.

338
00:21:31,280 --> 00:21:34,520
We both agreed last year
that we'll play against Xing Yao together.

339
00:21:36,160 --> 00:21:39,760
Do you know how helpless I felt...

340
00:21:42,280 --> 00:21:43,720
before the game?

341
00:21:46,480 --> 00:21:48,720
[exhales sharply]
I promise.

342
00:21:49,080 --> 00:21:50,440
I will be with you

343
00:21:51,200 --> 00:21:52,440
for every single game

344
00:21:53,520 --> 00:21:54,760
as long as you need me.

345
00:21:59,520 --> 00:22:00,640
All right.

346
00:22:01,040 --> 00:22:03,640
No other man can hear me
saying these words.

347
00:22:04,320 --> 00:22:08,560
We still have some unresolved problems,
but we will be partners again, right?

348
00:22:08,960 --> 00:22:09,800
Mm-hm.

349
00:22:12,800 --> 00:22:13,800
[chuckles softly]

350
00:22:15,320 --> 00:22:16,440
[man 1] Mu Siyang's film.

351
00:22:16,920 --> 00:22:18,160
Let's go.

352
00:22:40,320 --> 00:22:41,480
[sighs sharply]

353
00:22:42,120 --> 00:22:45,200
I'm willing to do anything
as long as the captain can recover.

354
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:47,600
[Siyang] What are you willing to do?

355
00:22:47,960 --> 00:22:48,800
Captain.

356
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:50,000
Are you okay?

357
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:51,680
I'm fine.

358
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:54,200
It's just that my old wounds recrudesced.

359
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:57,040
I just need to rest for a while.

360
00:22:57,640 --> 00:22:59,160
Don't fool us this time.

361
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:01,920
Right. You played with difficulty today.

362
00:23:02,320 --> 00:23:03,320
Are you really okay?

363
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:05,880
[sighs]

364
00:23:07,320 --> 00:23:08,880
Give me your hand.

365
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:10,040
Huh?

366
00:23:11,560 --> 00:23:14,320
It hurts! Your hand is okay!

367
00:23:14,400 --> 00:23:15,360
[groans]

368
00:23:16,240 --> 00:23:19,600
Now that the captain is okay
and we have beaten Xing Yao,

369
00:23:20,160 --> 00:23:22,680
let's celebrate at my place
and have some goose.

370
00:23:22,760 --> 00:23:23,760
That's great.

371
00:23:24,760 --> 00:23:25,720
Let's go.

372
00:23:26,280 --> 00:23:27,200
[soft chuckle]

373
00:23:36,560 --> 00:23:38,560
[light music]

374
00:23:40,760 --> 00:23:42,560
-[all] Cheers.
-Wait.

375
00:23:44,360 --> 00:23:45,720
Before that,

376
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:48,440
let me say something from my heart.

377
00:23:48,520 --> 00:23:49,400
Just a few words.

378
00:23:49,760 --> 00:23:52,200
Just think of it as a match summary.

379
00:23:52,280 --> 00:23:53,640
-[Qiao Chen] Okay.
-[Coach Qi] Mm.

380
00:23:54,680 --> 00:23:59,120
I know that many of you played
in the nationals last year.

381
00:23:59,720 --> 00:24:04,080
You played against Xing Yao
and ended up with pity and regret.

382
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:07,520
[Coach Qi] So you want to fulfill
your dream this year.

383
00:24:08,040 --> 00:24:10,920
You keep on training
even when you're graduating this year.

384
00:24:11,280 --> 00:24:14,600
And it is the first time for many of you
to play in the nationals this year.

385
00:24:15,480 --> 00:24:17,840
You are full of expectation and curiosity,

386
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:22,880
not knowing what obstacles
you will come across.

387
00:24:23,400 --> 00:24:26,200
But you got through that.

388
00:24:26,880 --> 00:24:29,320
You've become a strong team.

389
00:24:29,800 --> 00:24:31,520
As your coach,

390
00:24:31,600 --> 00:24:33,840
I'm very proud of you.

391
00:24:35,840 --> 00:24:39,160
We've had a lot of setbacks,

392
00:24:39,240 --> 00:24:44,400
but I believe these experiences
will give you new beginnings

393
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:46,000
and will make you stronger.

394
00:24:46,080 --> 00:24:48,440
You will become a better team.

395
00:24:48,960 --> 00:24:52,240
Let's move forward together.

396
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:54,760
Our aim is the national championship.

397
00:24:55,160 --> 00:24:56,120
Let's march on.

398
00:24:56,320 --> 00:24:57,280
That was so good.

399
00:24:57,680 --> 00:24:58,560
And short.

400
00:24:59,560 --> 00:25:01,560
When did you guys secretly eat the food?

401
00:25:03,440 --> 00:25:06,640
Oh. Coach, we didn't eat it secretly.

402
00:25:07,040 --> 00:25:07,880
You...

403
00:25:08,320 --> 00:25:11,360
Before the speech,

404
00:25:11,440 --> 00:25:13,280
you told us to eat while listening, right?

405
00:25:13,800 --> 00:25:15,840
-[chuckles softly]
-Why are you laughing?

406
00:25:16,840 --> 00:25:17,720
Because...

407
00:25:18,760 --> 00:25:20,200
Because he sounds just like you.

408
00:25:20,280 --> 00:25:23,440
-[Tang Jiale giggles]
-You think so? Let me do another one.

409
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:32,200
[quirky music]

410
00:25:35,000 --> 00:25:37,320
Anyone who loses

411
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:40,280
has to drink this.

412
00:25:43,520 --> 00:25:44,880
[Baiyang] Does it look familiar?

413
00:25:44,960 --> 00:25:47,440
This is you
when you force us to drink Yan-juice.

414
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:50,000
That's right.

415
00:25:50,080 --> 00:25:52,080
Hey, I got another one.

416
00:25:52,160 --> 00:25:53,160
[Tang Jiale clears throat]

417
00:25:55,840 --> 00:25:57,120
You still have a long way to go.

418
00:26:02,520 --> 00:26:03,960
[chuckles]

419
00:26:05,800 --> 00:26:06,640
How's that?

420
00:26:07,520 --> 00:26:08,920
It was no good.

421
00:26:09,000 --> 00:26:10,560
[Qiao Chen] Everyone can imitate Lu Xia.

422
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:12,920
Try someone who is difficult to imitate.

423
00:26:13,360 --> 00:26:15,120
How do you know he is imitating me?

424
00:26:16,000 --> 00:26:17,040
Tell me.

425
00:26:17,720 --> 00:26:19,680
You can try.

426
00:26:20,120 --> 00:26:20,960
[Qiao Chen] Fine.

427
00:26:30,240 --> 00:26:31,640
You still have a long way to go.

428
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:35,520
[laughing]

429
00:26:40,360 --> 00:26:43,840
-[chuckling]
-I've never said that.

430
00:26:43,920 --> 00:26:45,440
That's Lu Xia's line.

431
00:26:48,680 --> 00:26:50,280
What? You want to fight?

432
00:26:50,760 --> 00:26:52,000
[Tang Jiale laughs]

433
00:26:52,480 --> 00:26:53,680
Give me my bandana back.

434
00:26:53,760 --> 00:26:55,000
-[phone buzzes]
-[Baiyang scoffs]

435
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:57,680
[Baiyang] I can do it, too.

436
00:27:09,440 --> 00:27:10,480
Hello, doctor.

437
00:27:10,560 --> 00:27:12,320
[doctor 1] It was just
an initial examination.

438
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:13,400
The result was not good.

439
00:27:13,880 --> 00:27:15,040
Come to me again tomorrow.

440
00:27:15,520 --> 00:27:16,680
I have to warn you.

441
00:27:17,360 --> 00:27:18,920
There won't be another chance

442
00:27:19,240 --> 00:27:20,920
if you don't listen to me.

443
00:27:21,600 --> 00:27:22,480
Okay.

444
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:23,840
I know.

445
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:26,160
Thank you.

446
00:27:29,440 --> 00:27:31,440
[somber music]

447
00:27:34,440 --> 00:27:35,440
The weather's nice.

448
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:39,840
Oh.

449
00:27:44,520 --> 00:27:49,120
Um, thanks for winning the match
for Yu Qing.

450
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:53,240
Um... No.

451
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:54,960
I shouldn't say thank you.

452
00:27:55,520 --> 00:27:58,560
I should say congratulations.

453
00:27:59,960 --> 00:28:03,200
I believe that
you will keep moving on together.

454
00:28:03,760 --> 00:28:06,040
You will go farther and farther.

455
00:28:10,720 --> 00:28:12,920
[Ying gasps]
It's a meteor shower.

456
00:28:14,840 --> 00:28:16,160
[chuckles softly]

457
00:28:19,120 --> 00:28:21,120
[light music]

458
00:28:26,680 --> 00:28:28,000
[Ying] I have a wish.

459
00:28:28,480 --> 00:28:30,760
I wish Yu Qing can win

460
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:33,000
the national championship.

461
00:28:37,360 --> 00:28:39,360
[calm music]

462
00:28:54,360 --> 00:28:56,360
[gasps]

463
00:28:56,440 --> 00:28:58,840
Look at that. It's shining brightly.

464
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:00,880
[Tang Jiale chuckles]

465
00:29:01,280 --> 00:29:03,040
-[Tang Jiale] How beautiful.
-[Dayong] Uh-huh.

466
00:29:05,080 --> 00:29:07,080
[calm music]

467
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:25,600
We can make a wish.

468
00:29:26,200 --> 00:29:27,160
Yes.

469
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:43,960
YU QING

470
00:29:44,400 --> 00:29:45,400
[both grunting]

471
00:29:45,840 --> 00:29:47,080
This one. Turn the page.

472
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:48,640
-What's good?
-This.

473
00:29:54,600 --> 00:29:57,520
[grunting]

474
00:29:59,640 --> 00:30:00,840
Is everyone here?

475
00:30:01,320 --> 00:30:03,120
Oh. Siyang isn't here.

476
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:06,520
Coach.

477
00:30:07,320 --> 00:30:08,800
I have something to tell you.

478
00:30:09,760 --> 00:30:11,200
Starting today,

479
00:30:11,400 --> 00:30:13,920
Siyang will leave the club for a while.

480
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:15,440
What?

481
00:30:16,440 --> 00:30:18,440
[somber music]

482
00:30:27,680 --> 00:30:29,760
[doctor 1] You didn't need surgery before.

483
00:30:30,200 --> 00:30:31,480
But I believe

484
00:30:32,240 --> 00:30:34,960
you knew it well after that game.

485
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:37,840
[doctor 1] If you don't hurry up
and receive treatment,

486
00:30:39,120 --> 00:30:42,160
it may cause permanent damage
to your arms.

487
00:30:43,320 --> 00:30:44,800
A decision must be made quickly.

488
00:30:45,640 --> 00:30:47,200
You have to take the surgerysoon.

489
00:30:48,440 --> 00:30:51,080
Or else you may not be able
to play tennis,

490
00:30:51,520 --> 00:30:53,600
let alone play a match.

491
00:30:53,960 --> 00:30:57,000
If you continue like this,
the consequence will be really bad.

492
00:30:58,520 --> 00:30:59,480
I know.

493
00:31:00,480 --> 00:31:03,040
I will do any kind of examination
you arrange for me.

494
00:31:03,640 --> 00:31:05,880
YU QING

495
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:08,640
[Dayong] You are asking for a leave?

496
00:31:08,720 --> 00:31:09,720
[Zhuo Zhi] Yes.

497
00:31:10,560 --> 00:31:11,960
My good friend got sick.

498
00:31:12,520 --> 00:31:14,080
He didn't tell me before.

499
00:31:14,680 --> 00:31:16,600
It suddenly occurred
when he was taking the exam.

500
00:31:17,040 --> 00:31:18,080
I would like to visit him.

501
00:31:19,320 --> 00:31:20,560
How could that be?

502
00:31:20,640 --> 00:31:21,880
Is he okay now?

503
00:31:22,280 --> 00:31:23,280
I don't know.

504
00:31:23,600 --> 00:31:24,840
The result will come out today.

505
00:31:25,560 --> 00:31:26,400
[sighs]

506
00:31:27,480 --> 00:31:28,600
Hurry off then.

507
00:31:28,680 --> 00:31:31,120
Just send me a message
in these types of situations.

508
00:31:31,200 --> 00:31:32,040
-Mm-hm.
-Okay?

509
00:31:35,760 --> 00:31:37,560
-Take care.
-[Zhuo Zhi] Sure.

510
00:31:39,800 --> 00:31:40,880
[sighs]

511
00:31:47,480 --> 00:31:48,760
A good friend?

512
00:31:49,360 --> 00:31:54,720
Don't you think the friend
he described sounds familiar?

513
00:31:56,280 --> 00:31:57,160
Huh?

514
00:31:57,440 --> 00:31:59,080
[Dayong] Do you know any of his friends?

515
00:31:59,160 --> 00:32:00,120
Is that your classmate?

516
00:32:01,200 --> 00:32:02,160
Oh.

517
00:32:02,880 --> 00:32:03,800
I know!

518
00:32:04,320 --> 00:32:07,080
The one he was talking about
is our captain.

519
00:32:07,520 --> 00:32:08,480
Our captain?

520
00:32:10,600 --> 00:32:11,560
Zhuo Zhi.

521
00:32:13,720 --> 00:32:14,880
Zhuo Zhi.

522
00:32:16,720 --> 00:32:17,760
Where is Zhuo Zhi?

523
00:32:18,120 --> 00:32:20,120
-[Tang Jiale] I have no idea.
-Let's practice first.

524
00:32:20,560 --> 00:32:22,960
The captain would say so if he was here.

525
00:32:25,560 --> 00:32:30,840
COURT P6

526
00:32:31,600 --> 00:32:32,680
[sighs]

527
00:32:38,080 --> 00:32:39,120
[sighs sharply]

528
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:42,720
Hmm?

529
00:32:45,480 --> 00:32:46,480
Little Lu Xia.

530
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:49,960
Take line 5 to Xiang Jiang Station,
then change to line 10,

531
00:32:50,040 --> 00:32:52,680
go out from exit B
of the People's Hospital, then turn left.

532
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:54,400
You saw him?

533
00:32:55,120 --> 00:32:56,040
Look at you.

534
00:32:56,120 --> 00:32:57,880
Just say it if you want to visit Siyang.

535
00:32:57,960 --> 00:33:00,760
Why do you have to secretly check the way?
You want to go alone?

536
00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:04,240
You are far from finishing
the training volume.

537
00:33:04,880 --> 00:33:07,200
No chatting.
Let's go together after training.

538
00:33:09,880 --> 00:33:11,880
[quirky music]

539
00:33:18,600 --> 00:33:21,600
Sir, your fried rice is ready.

540
00:33:21,840 --> 00:33:22,760
[Siyang] Wait.

541
00:33:30,560 --> 00:33:32,520
[sighs]
What did the doctor say?

542
00:33:35,000 --> 00:33:36,000
[groans]

543
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:41,760
Will it kill you to say "please"?

544
00:33:47,800 --> 00:33:49,800
[somber music]

545
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:53,880
[exhales sharply]

546
00:34:09,560 --> 00:34:11,040
What did the doctor say?

547
00:34:12,679 --> 00:34:14,520
Oh. Sit down.

548
00:34:21,040 --> 00:34:22,560
I'll ask him if you don't tell me.

549
00:34:25,199 --> 00:34:27,480
The doctor said that my situation...

550
00:34:28,400 --> 00:34:29,520
is not good.

551
00:34:29,840 --> 00:34:31,840
[somber music]

552
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:33,400
[exhales sharply]

553
00:34:35,239 --> 00:34:37,120
[Siyang grunting]

554
00:34:41,679 --> 00:34:42,800
[sighs]

555
00:34:44,440 --> 00:34:45,560
[Siyang grunts]

556
00:34:46,560 --> 00:34:47,719
Have you thought about it?

557
00:34:48,280 --> 00:34:50,360
What if you can't play tennis anymore?

558
00:34:51,199 --> 00:34:52,040
[sighs]

559
