and perseverance.

581
00:36:00,920 --> 00:36:02,760
[Siyang] Not only from this game,

582
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:05,280
I saw everyone was growing

583
00:36:05,920 --> 00:36:08,800
since the beginning
of the regulation match.

584
00:36:09,640 --> 00:36:11,640
