600
00:36:54,520 --> 00:36:55,480
And me?

601
00:36:56,080 --> 00:36:57,440
In about ten minutes.

602
00:36:57,520 --> 00:36:58,400
How about Lu Xia?

603
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:01,640
Lu Xia won't have time to visit him.

604
00:37:01,720 --> 00:37:02,840
How about tomorrow at noon?

605
